{"tid":1745294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】香港伊利沙伯中學生向英女皇發公開信 望能在香港危機上Connect","createTime":"2019-11-22T06:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T02:34:55.000Z","uid":92301,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c5add5fd3abd89fce0e911d5c1ad2943646b8ce0","tid":1745294,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"修訂《逃犯條例》所引起的抗爭運動已逾5個月，美國參議院亦通過《香港人權與民主法案》。香港伊利沙伯中學有學生去信英女皇「求救」，指自己是背負女皇之名（伊利沙伯二世），並謹遵校訓「修己善群」之教誨，希望在英國戰線上略盡綿力。<br />\n<br />\n公開信提到，香港多月來抗爭的嚴峻情況，特區政府強行修訂《逃犯條例》，草案將容許內地政府合法地將港人拘捕，惟內地以腐敗，壓迫異見人士，侵犯人權和缺乏法治而聞名，故引起港人的擔憂及不滿。特區政府試圖通過立法機構強制執行法案，甚至無視200萬名港人和平表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n信件又提到，香港警察濫權濫捕的情況，無差別地暴力對待示威者、記者、義務急救員等，甚至無視國際對使用催淚彈、胡椒噴霧、橡膠子彈的指引。有女被捕人士被捕後遭警輪姦成孕，並在伊利沙伯醫院墮胎，以及過去高達256宗無法解釋的自殺和及2537宗發現屍體的案件；以至科大學生周梓樂因警封鎖救護車20分鐘，而延誤治療，中大和理大的保衞之戰等，強調港人的現況是「We are in fear of our lives」。<br />\n<br />\n公開信指，英國與香港有緊密的經濟、歷史文化等關係，希望英國能繼續支持香港人爭取自由和民主，並通過將英國版的《香港人權與民主法》，對中國違反中英聯合聲明的問題作出堅定的反應，冀望能與女王在香港危機上 「Connect」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mAXmTqZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmAXmTqZ.jpg&h=3c74eae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yPTKxJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yPTKxJ.jpg&h=de0814ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191122/60295036?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191122%2F60295036%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyliZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=332d12a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191122%2F60295036%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=916b24c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191122/60295036?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"3990a67866d20daa0abe857ca5972b0479ba04bd","tid":1745294,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c988314b1198e9d0fbe35df01c655791805d7c","tid":1745294,"uid":81627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:55:58.000Z","msg":"啲英文...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d060a3c1f4a5ac9c9b2259c2deeb1f3c985a31c","tid":1745294,"uid":283385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:02:23.000Z","msg":"好多字，btw加油！"},{"pid":"ccedc4464eff29cd900dd20a2fb9a73649ff4015","tid":1745294,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:16:56.000Z","msg":"學英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f2c1273473884b1890e41a6687c1e84521148c","tid":1745294,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:18:40.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲靠日落帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n爆親大獲野一味達式關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未做過實事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113b333026f600f0b068c78cb6b416c1132a47a2","tid":1745294,"uid":249525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:41:21.000Z","msg":"唉，女皇冇實權的，俾佢有無用？"},{"pid":"d599647860c813a648ac579b354a21136f8e939e","tid":1745294,"uid":81424,